# ShiftSync Environment Variables

# ==========================================
# OpenAI API Key (OPTIONAL)
# ==========================================
# Get your key here: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
#
# - If set:   The app uses GPT-4o to analyze your CSV headers and
#             generate real-time schema mappings with confidence scores.
# - If empty: The app falls back to built-in demo mappings automatically.
#             Everything still works — upload, visual graph, validation,
#             and export — using pre-configured mapping rules.
#
# TL;DR: Leave blank for demo mode, add a key for live AI mapping.
OPENAI_API_KEY=

# ==========================================
# Alternative Providers (Requires Code Changes)
# ==========================================
# To use Anthropic or Gemini instead of OpenAI, you'll need to modify
# 'app/api/map/route.ts' to use their respective SDKs.
#
# GEMINI_API_KEY=          # https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=       # https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
